com.acrolinx.javasdk.gui

Interface DialogsPresenter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ColorDialogPresenter, ContextMenuPresenter, ErrorBoxDialogPresenter, KeyWordsDialogPresenter, MessageBoxDialogPresenter, ServerDialogPresenter, SetContextMenuPresenter, WebPagePresenter

    public interface DialogsPresenter
extends MessageBoxDialogPresenter, WebPagePresenter, ContextMenuPresenter, SetContextMenuPresenter, ServerDialogPresenter, ColorDialogPresenter, KeyWordsDialogPresenter, ErrorBoxDialogPresenter
    The interface DialogsPresenter is used for displaying all kinds of dialogs used by the Acrolinx Java SDK.

      static class  DialogsPresenter.OptionsArea
